---
title: Haloumi & Chargrilled Capsicum Burger with Potato Wedges
description: Prepare to fall in love with haloumi all over again when you taste this irresistible burger. We've teamed the cheesy favourite with chargrilled capsicum relish and caramelised onion so there's lots of delicious flavour going on, plus sliced tomato and salad leaves for a fresh touch. With potato wedges on the side, this dinner is totally dishy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d12e5deeed6fc000b266e1e-8fa43acc.jpg
